I've taken both, it is true that they cover similiar material the main difference is the expectations of the final projects & the other people taking the course. 

I'd say if you are debating taking one or the other and are not a grad student, take 194-15. If you have specific questions about it, post a follow up

AFAIK 194-15 covered GPU programming a bit more than 267 (but both classes do have it)
